organic.title: National Domestic Violence Hotline: Domestic Violence Support
organic.snippet: Everyone deserves relationships free from domestic violence. When you're ready, we're here to listen with confidential support 24/7/365.

organic.title: Salvation Army: Hickman House | United Way of King County
organic.snippet: Hickman House is a transitional housing and rapid re-housing program that provides a safe place and additional time for domestic violence survivors.

organic.title: Domestic Violence Programs and Shelters - Seattle Social Services
organic.snippet: The Salvation Army Domestic Violence Services, based in King County, provide assistance to families whose lives have been affected by domestic abuse.
